data.description: Buyers Financing fell through-Cozy SINGLE STORY in CYPRESSWOOD. This 3-2 has new LVP flooring, carpet and interior paint.  Livingroom features gas fireplace. Kitchen has center island with GAS cooktop and separate butlers pantry. Large backyard is divided with covered back patio and separate gated area for garden, animals, or whatever your imagination cooks up.
